===Pronunciation===
*ἀμήν / amēn / am-ane'
=== Etymology ===

Of Hebrew origin [[אמן]] {{HH|543}}; properly firm, that is, (figuratively) trustworthy;
=== Adverb ===
adverbially surely (often as interjection so be it): 
[[amen]], [[verily]].